action.description: From printer. To re-engrossment. Re-engrossed. Third reprint. To Assembly.In Assembly.Returned from Assembly in accordance with motion of the body.Returned to Senate.In Senate.Action of passage rescinded.Placed on General File.Read third time. Amended. (Amend. No. 34.)Reprinting dispensed with.Read third time. Passed, as amended. Title approved, as amended. (Yeas: 16, Nays: 2, Excused: 3.) To printer.From printer. To re-engrossment. Re-engrossed. Fourth reprint. To Assembly.In Assembly.Senate Amendment Nos. 31 and 34 concurred in. To enrollment.
